| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2020-0207 — Recovery Inhibition (revil)"
| comment "Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: c690a9b8-9b2a-52ed-b617-9abc1ae2eb64"
